<indexterm><primary>HTMLTableMain</primary><secondary>tryAddHeader</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>tryAddHeader ( )</computeroutput></para>
<para>Internal test to see if we can add an header. For instance, we can only add a super header to a table if there is no group defined. And we can only create a sub Header to a group if it contains no row </para>
<para>
Réimplémentée à partir de <link linkend="_class_h_t_m_l_table_base_1a84111cacd5c00c7fab4f4a28a97ce63b">HTMLTableBase</link>.</para>
